You can also use hotkeys to add paths (

        Enter
      ), move paths up and down (

        Ctrl
        arrow up/down
      ), send a path to the top of the list (

        Ctrl
        Home
      ) and send a path to the bottom of the list (

        Ctrl
        End
    ).

